"Change Set:		9835SUnit-ul.75SUnit-ul.75:- run long test cases by default"!!LongTestCase class methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ul 3/27/2010 21:45'!shouldRun	<preference: 'Run long test cases'		category: 'SUnit'		description: 'If true, the tests defined in subclasses of LongTestCase will run, if they are selected in the Test Runner, otherwise not. As the name suggests, running these tests can take a long time.'		type: #Boolean>	^ShouldRun ifNil: [ true ]! !